LOCUS       SpyTag002                 14 aa            linear   UNK 01-JAN-1980
DEFINITION  SpyTag002 — second-generation 14-aa peptide tag (VPTIVMVDAYKRYK)
            that forms a spontaneous, irreversible isopeptide bond to
            SpyCatcher002, reacting ~12x faster than the original SpyTag..
